These are Puzzles for 1x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-1::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, train, snowmobile, bike, jet-ski
1. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2  |   3   |   4   |  5  |
| Transport   | snowmobile | trike | bike | train | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, water-polo, skiing, cycling, handball
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |     3     |     4     |     5      |
| Sport   | cycling | handball | water-polo | swimming | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, r&b, disco, house, hip-hop
1. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
3. the fan of salsa is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |  3   |     4      |   5   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | disco | salsa | house | hip-hop |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-4::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: apricot, blue, brown, orange, ebony
1. the person who likes apricot is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |       1       |     2     |       3        |   4    |     5     |
| Color   | orange | blue | brown | ebony | apricot |

