.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-5::.
There are 5 different nationalities: polish, british, colombian, french, egyptian
1. the egyptian is in an even position##4
2. the egyptian is on the left of the colombian##1
3. the polish is on the right of the british##1
4. the british is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |  2   |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| Nationality   | french | egyptian | colombian | british | polish |

