.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: western, romance, disaster, satire, spy
1. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is between the person watching western movies and the person watching satire movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3    |    4     |  5   |
| Movie-Genre   | western | disaster | satire | romance | spy |

