2. the aristoff-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the chaman-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |     2      |   3   |    4     |    5    |
| Cigar   | chaman | alhambra | bolivar | aristoff | oliveros |

