.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-9::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, woodworking, filmmaking, skydiving, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
6. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |   2   |   3   |  4   |     5      |
| Hobby   | traveling | filmmaking | woodworking | chess | skydiving |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-10::.
