.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, spy, romance, fantasy, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching romance movies##2
2. the person watching fantasy movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2  |    3     |    4     |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | zombie | romance | fantasy | mystery |

 